_sText:
Eyo bois!

The moment everyone has been waiting for.
Eon is out at last and everyone can finally enjoy some decent surf, after years and years of terrible maps :^)

Jokes aside though this is my first ever released map.
It includes the linear map which is about tier 4-5.
It also has 3 bonuses which are made by myself, horsefeathers and say wat (order of the actual bonuses).

BTW. special f00ken shoutout to horse who has almost taught me basically everything I know about mapping and helped me with lots of problems that I encountered while making this map.

I hope to make more maps in the future.
Happy surfing noobs.

P.S. I hope you like it Syncronyze :^)
P.P.S. Say Wat plis cumback!
